properties.areaDesc: Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island
properties.headline: Winter Storm Warning issued January 25 at 11:52AM AKST until January 25 at 9:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Heavy snow. Additional snow accumulations of 5 to 7
inches.

* WHERE...Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM AKST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Travel will be very difficult. Visibilities will be
reduced during periods of heavier snow. Heavy wet snow will be
difficult to manage.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Snow will transition to rain this evening,
extending impacts beyond the time when snow is accumulating.
properties.instruction:
If you must travel, keep an extra flashlight, food, and water in
your vehicle in case of an emergency.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER STORM WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM AKST THIS EVENING FOR JUNEAU BOROUGH
